name: Anaerobic Intensive 30sec #3
description:
Today we step up the effort, but only briefly. By completing 6 x 30-second high-intensity efforts, we will be tapping into our anaerobic reserves while recruiting a large number of fast-twitch fibres. 



With plenty of recovery between efforts, you should be hitting each interval fully recovered.
